[TestInjectDiagnostics/far_right_caret_wraps_long_message_on_left - 1]

expr: sum(foo) without(colo_id, instance, node_type, region, node_status, job, colo_name)

2 | expr: sum(foo) without(colo_id, instance, node_type, region, node_status, job, colo_name)
                                                                                         ^^^^
           Using `without(colo_id, instance, node_type, region, node_status, job, colo_name)`
           removes all these labels from the results.

